{"tha-ap130:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap130:0.2":"Sereyyavagga ","tha-ap130:0.3":"8 Nanasannikattheraapadana ","tha-ap130:1.1":"“Pabbate himavantamhi, ","tha-ap130:1.2":"vasami pabbatantare; ","tha-ap130:1.3":"Pulinam sobhanam disva, ","tha-ap130:1.4":"buddhasettham anussarim. ","tha-ap130:2.1":"Nane upanidha natthi, ","tha-ap130:2.2":"sankharam natthi satthuno; ","tha-ap130:2.3":"Sabbadhammam abhinnaya, ","tha-ap130:2.4":"nanena adhimuccati. ","tha-ap130:3.1":"Namo te purisajanna, ","tha-ap130:3.2":"namo te purisuttama; ","tha-ap130:3.3":"Nanena te samo natthi, ","tha-ap130:3.4":"yavata nanamuttamam. ","tha-ap130:4.1":"Nane cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap130:4.2":"kappam saggamhi modaham; ","tha-ap130:4.3":"Avasesesu kappesu, ","tha-ap130:4.4":"kusalam caritam maya. ","tha-ap130:5.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap130:5.2":"yam sannamalabhim tada; ","tha-ap130:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap130:5.4":"nanasannayidam phalam. ","tha-ap130:6.1":"Ito sattatikappamhi, ","tha-ap130:6.2":"eko pulinapupphiyo; ","tha-ap130:6.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap130:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap130:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap130:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap130:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap130:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nanasanniko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap130:9.1":"Nanasannikattherassapadanam atthamam. "}